{"tid":352600,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"大阪行程求推介","createTime":"2017-08-09T01:32:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-18T09:41:41.000Z","uid":42646,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1e2801e10e2ffe5025f9f23811bcdd0bf4e906ba","tid":352600,"uid":42646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T01:32:10.000Z","msg":"黎緊10月27至11月2會去大阪<br />\n早機6點到關西機場<br />\n<br />\n10月27 - 六甲山牧場&gt;姬路城&gt;有馬溫泉過夜<br />\n10月28 - 明石大橋&gt;白濱溫泉酒店過夜<br />\n10月29 - 白濱一日遊&gt;難波酒店過夜<br />\n10月30 - <span style=\"color: red;\">係大阪未諗</span><br />\n10月31 - USJ<br />\n11月1   - <span style=\"color: red;\">係大阪未諗</span><br />\n11月2   - 17:00機返香港<br />\n<br />\n主要想幫手諗31號同1號做d咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n通天閣，梅田藍天大廈，清水寺，八坂神社，黑門市場，錦市場，大阪今昔館，嵐山，伏見稻荷，<span style=\"color: red;\">以上嘅都去過唔打算再去</span><br />\n<br />\n暫時只諗到去朝日啤酒廠/大阪杯麵博物館/宇治/金閣寺/貴船鞍馬<br />\n<br />\n不過都想聽下其他巴打嘅建議<br />\n<br />\n利申: 認真post，唔洗講飛田新地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n( 兩個男人去，唔好答我摩天輪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )"},{"pid":"7e0e36f709bf9f883a7d75fc8f0a7b08b6643437","tid":352600,"uid":42646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T01:36:05.000Z","msg":"另外，兩個男人去海遊館，會唔會太on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5b799a34b615342ede2b6e7cb3c5aeb879d46c1","tid":352600,"uid":8014,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T01:48:59.000Z","msg":"你搞gay? 兩個男人唔去飛田新地反而bk 溫泉酒店格劍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"270345b1a01362ddce2b6c6b74068daac474409c","tid":352600,"uid":42646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T01:51:10.000Z","msg":"唔係搞gay<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 兄弟嘅野，冇所謂啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hk